---
tags: [ git, tui ]
---
# Global
?           Help / keybindings
q           Quit / go back
Esc         Cancel / close
<C-r>       Switch repo
+           Next screen mode (normal/half/full)
_           Previous screen mode

# Navigation
h/l         Switch panels (left/right)
j/k         Move up/down in list
[/]         Switch tabs
{/}         Scroll diff up/down
<C-d/u>     Scroll main panel (half page)

# Files Panel (1)
Space       Stage/unstage file
a           Stage all / unstage all
d           View 'discard changes' options
e           Edit file in editor
o           Open file
c           Commit staged changes
A           Amend last commit
i           Add to .gitignore

# Branches Panel (2)
Space       Checkout branch
n           New branch
d           Delete branch
r           Rebase current branch onto selected
M           Merge selected into current
f           Fast-forward to upstream
c           Checkout by name

# Commits Panel (3)
Space       Checkout commit
r           Revert commit
R           Rename commit (reword)
g           View reset options
s           Squash down
f           Fixup commit
d           Drop commit
e           Edit commit
p           Pick commit (when rebasing)
t           Create tag
<C-j/k>     Move commit up/down (when rebasing)

# Stash Panel (4)
Space       Apply stash
g           Pop stash
d           Drop stash
n           New stash

# Staging View
Enter       Stage individual lines/hunks
a           Stage all hunks
d           Discard hunk
e           Edit hunk

# Remotes
f           Fetch remote
p           Pull from remote
P           Push to remote
u           Set upstream

# Searching
/           Start search
n/N         Next/prev search result

# Misc
m           View merge/rebase options
x           Open command menu
z           Undo (reflog)
<C-z>       Redo (reflog)
@           Open command log
:           Execute custom command
